Output demos/gif3_t2s.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Shell "zsh"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms

Hide
Type "export PATH=/Users/nik/github/project-alpha/target/debug:$PATH"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "rpg -d demo_saas"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "\version"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "\t2s"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "how many orders were placed in the last 7 days"
Enter
Sleep 6s

Enter
Sleep 2s

Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "\yolo"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "how many orders were placed in the last 7 days"
Enter
Sleep 8s

Sleep 3s
